{
  "id": "RAW_5e1b60",
  "title": "对话李飞飞：AI 不仅是工具，更是塑造人类未来的力量",
  "url": "http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkzNjkzNDMzMA==&mid=2247483852&idx=1&sn=dc9212c12f03a611402d526006b33d2a",
  "date": "2025-05-16 06:47:00",
  "author": "(yikai 的摸鱼笔记)",
  "siteName": "yikai 的摸鱼笔记",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <section style=\"\">\n   <section style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:20px 25px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);margin:25px 0;\">\n    <h2 style=\"color:#546A7B;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">核心要点</span></h2>\n    <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:15px 0 5px;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.6;\">\n      <section>\n       <span leaf=\"\">AI已成为一项文明级别的技术，其发展必须以人为本，关注个体福祉、社群赋能和社会整体进步。</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.6;\">\n      <section>\n       <span leaf=\"\">好奇心与科技向善的信念是驱动AI研究与创新的“北极星”。</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.6;\">\n      <section>\n       <span leaf=\"\">空间智能是AI发展的下一个重要前沿，对理解和交互三维世界至关重要，将在创造、教育、机器人等领域发挥巨大作用。</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.6;\">\n      <section>\n       <span leaf=\"\">健康的AI生态系统需要公共与私营部门的平衡发展，重视基础研究、人才培养、开源社区及负责任的政策引导。</span>\n      </section></li>\n     <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;line-height:1.6;\">\n      <section>\n       <span leaf=\"\">AI时代亟需加强公众教育，提升信息辨别能力，防范虚假信息，确保技术发展惠及所有人和整个社会。</span>\n      </section></li>\n    </ul>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"border-radius:6px;padding:20px 25px;box-shadow:0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);margin:25px 0;\">\n    <h2 style=\"color:#546A7B;font-size:18px;font-weight:500;margin-top:0;margin-bottom:15px;\"><span leaf=\"\">背景</span></h2>\n    <p style=\"margin:15px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">本期《High Signal》播客由Delphina出品，主持人Hugo Bowne-Anderson对话李飞飞（Fei-Fei Li）。李飞飞是斯坦福大学以人为本AI研究所（HAI）的联合主任，AI领域的权威学者。本期节目深入探讨了AI从ImageNet的早期突破到基础模型的崛起，重点讨论了</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">空间智能</span></span><span leaf=\"\">作为AI下一重大转变的潜力，以及</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">“以人为本的AI”如何在实践中落地，以及AI作为一项文明技术如何塑造个体、社区乃至整个社会。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">Delphina致力于构建AI数据科学家，加速数据、机器学习和AI的应用。</span></p>\n   </section>\n   <section style=\"margin-top:30px;\">\n    <section style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">\n     <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.2px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9jtbpvw10ew\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;visibility: visible;\">本文约 5000 字，预估阅读时间为 10 分钟。</span></p>\n     <p style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;color:rgb(51, 51, 51);white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:17px;min-height:1em;box-sizing:border-box !important;text-decoration-thickness:initial;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent;outline:0px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:-apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:center;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:0px;margin:0px;visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.2px;clear:both;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;max-width:100%;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"m9jtbpvwiks\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;outline: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;visibility: visible;\">您也可以在<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">小宇宙</span>上听本期播客内容（点击底部阅读原文）</span></p>\n     <h2 style=\"color:#7A9E9F;font-weight:500;margin-top:35px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.4;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5;\"><span leaf=\"\">01 引言：AI——改变人类文明的技术</span></h2>\n     <section style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n      <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n       <span style=\"color:#8B9BAA;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #8B9BAA;\"><span leaf=\"\">Duncan Gilchrist</span></span>\n       <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">在Delphina，我们主要研发用于数据科学领域的AI智能体。基于工作性质，我们经常接触该领域的顶尖专家，因此希望通过这档播客，与大家分享真正有价值的高含金量内容。</span></p>\n        <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">在我的职业生涯中，我一直把AI和机器学习当作效能杠杆——优化模型、提升指标、逐步推动业务发展。但飞飞一句话让我醍醐灌顶，</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">她说AI是足以改变人类文明的技术。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">它不是某个功能，不是某个行业，而是从就业市场到国际关系，甚至整个社会架构都将被其重塑的技术。</span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n       <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n       <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n        <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">我们与飞飞的对话非常精彩。她认为AI是改变人类文明的技术，但发展AI必须坚守人文价值。</span></p>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n     <section style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">\n      <h2 style=\"color:#7A9E9F;font-weight:500;margin-top:35px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.4;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5;\"><span leaf=\"\">02 科研之路与北极星：李飞飞的探索与坚持</span></h2>\n      <section style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n       <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n        <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n        <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">飞飞，您从科研到创业再到教育，经历特别丰富。这一路上有哪些特别关键的节点？</span></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n        <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n        <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">回顾我的历程，第一个重要转折点是找到真正热爱的事业方向。我最初热爱物理，之后在博士期间接触到AI研究，那时还是AI的起步阶段，甚至被称为“AI寒冬”。</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">但真正让我震撼的是，我发现这门科学直指智能的本质。</span></span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">当然，</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">ImageNet</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的出现无疑是个重大转折点。从构思到实施，在无人看好的情况下坚持数年，直到ImageNet挑战赛带来了深度学习的革命性突破。大约在2018年，我意识到AI已不再仅仅是个人兴趣，它已成为一种</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">文明级技术</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，带来了巨大的希望、机遇和深远影响。那一刻我决定回到斯坦福大学建立“</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以人为本AI研究所</span></span><span leaf=\"\">”（HAI），推广以人类价值为核心的AI发展理念。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">最近，我创立了</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">World Labs实验室</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，与顶尖专家共同在生成式AI领域打造前所未有的技术和产品，这同样是一个激动人心的挑战。</span></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n        <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n        <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">这一路走来，从物理学到计算机视觉，再到ImageNet，直至如今AI的突破，并非一帆风顺。是什么在指引您前行，又是如何捕捉到关键路标的？</span></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n        <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n        <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">科研和创业之路从不是直线。我最近在书《我眼中的世界》中提到，指引方向的</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">北极星</span></span><span leaf=\"\">对我而言就是</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">好奇心</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。我一直保持着追随好奇心的勇气，它能突破自我，看到更广阔的世界。我的好奇心始终聚焦在智能科学，特别是创造智能机器。</span></p>\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">随着研究深入，我逐渐形成了另一个重要信念：科技应该向善。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">这种乐观态度让我始终坚持以人为本，坚守人文价值。这就像第二个方向标，继续为我指引前路。</span></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n        <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n        <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">当好奇心可以带您去任何地方时，如何确定专注点？</span></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n        <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n        <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n         <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">关键有两点：第一要选一个够大胆的难题，是那种暂时无解的；第二这个问题要能像物理学里那样，给你指明探索方向。我着迷于那些悬而未决的重大难题，然后让好奇心带着我一路探索。</span></p>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n      <section style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">\n       <h2 style=\"color:#7A9E9F;font-weight:500;margin-top:35px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.4;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5;\"><span leaf=\"\">03 以人为本AI的内涵：从个体到社会的三重关怀</span></h2>\n       <section style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n        <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n         <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n         <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n          <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">您经常提到“以人为中心”，这在当前AI系统中该如何定义？</span></p>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n         <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n         <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n          <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">在我看来，“</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">以人为中心</span></span><span leaf=\"\">”是AI发展的指路明灯。核心原则是：AI技术和产品要能造福全人类和每个个体，并符合社会价值观。我将其概括为三个同心圆：</span></p>\n          <ol style=\"padding-left:1.8em;margin:16px 0;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n           <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;padding-left:0.3em;line-height:1.6;\">\n            <section>\n             <span leaf=\"\">个体层面：技术应帮助每个人改善生活，维护人的尊严。例如，在医疗健康领域，智能设备可以改善老年人和长期病患的生活，但必须警惕侵犯隐私或剥夺个人选择权的问题，始终将个人价值、尊严和人文关怀置于核心。</span>\n            </section></li>\n           <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;padding-left:0.3em;line-height:1.6;\">\n            <section>\n             <span leaf=\"\">社群层面：AI技术应支持社群发展，增强人类能力。例如，在生成式AI与创作者的关系中，技术应赋能而非取代或剥夺创作者的权益。</span>\n            </section></li>\n           <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;padding-left:0.3em;line-height:1.6;\">\n            <section>\n             <span leaf=\"\">社会层面：</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI作为一项改变人类文明进程的突破性技术，正深刻影响就业、政府运作和国际格局。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">我们需要思考如何与立法者合作，让民众参与，避免技术加剧社会对立，确保发展成果惠及所有人。这是AI人本化发展必须面对的重大社会课题。</span>\n            </section></li>\n          </ol>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n         <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n         <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n          <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">是什么样的经历让您形成了这种“以人为中心”的理念？</span></p>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n         <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n         <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n          <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">15岁移民美国的经历是我成长的关键时期。面对全新社会和语言文化的冲击，我感受到了许多陌生人的善意，特别是我的高中数学老师Bob Sabella一家，这在我心中种下了珍贵的人生观。后来进入AI领域，导师、同事们的求知欲和支持氛围也深深影响了我。</span></p>\n          <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，我母亲的经历也至关重要。她体弱多病，我长期照顾她，经历了各种医疗场景。但她对科学的热爱和对我的支持，让我明白了什么才是真正值得珍惜的。这些经历让我亲眼看到人性中最闪光的部分——发自内心的善良，并始终相信这种美好。</span></p>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n       <section style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">\n        <h2 style=\"color:#7A9E9F;font-weight:500;margin-top:35px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.4;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5;\"><span leaf=\"\">04 AI赋能未来：医疗、教育及更多领域的应用前景</span></h2>\n        <section style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n         <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n          <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n          <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n           <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">在哪些应用领域，最能体现人本主义AI发展路径的重要性？</span></p>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n         <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n          <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n          <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n           <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">AI具有跨领域特性，几乎所有领域都需要人本理念。</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">医疗健康</span></span><span leaf=\"\">领域是典型，如环境监测传感器、智能清洁机器人、诊断设备等，尤其关注帮助弱势群体。</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">可持续发展</span></span><span leaf=\"\">和</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">气候变化</span></span><span leaf=\"\">也是重要领域，AI在生物多样性测绘、海洋探索、气候模拟中大有可为，例如劳伦斯实验室的核聚变突破就得益于机器学习算法。</span></p>\n           <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">教育领域</span></span><span leaf=\"\">潜力巨大。当前的教育体系亟待革新，信息编码、传输和分发方式已发生巨变。</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成式AI为我们提供了实现终身学习的工具，这是人工智能应用中特别以人为本的典范。</span></span></p>\n           <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">农业领域</span></span><span leaf=\"\">如何提高效率、解放人力，以及</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">政府系统</span></span><span leaf=\"\">如何用AI提升公共服务效率，都是AI大展身手的深刻变革领域。每个行业都能找到以人为中心的AI应用场景。</span></p>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n        <section style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">\n         <h2 style=\"color:#7A9E9F;font-weight:500;margin-top:35px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.4;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5;\"><span leaf=\"\">05 空间智能：AI的下一个前沿与三维世界建模</span></h2>\n         <section style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">您长期专注于空间智能领域，能否解释一下什么是</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">空间智能AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\">？为什么它如此重要？</span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">空间智能</span></span><span leaf=\"\">是构成完整智能（无论是AI还是AGI）的重要拼图。理解三维空间、与之互动、在其中创造和创新，这些能力是人类智能的基础，也将成为未来智能体的核心能力。其核心在于</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">三维建模</span></span><span leaf=\"\">，用数学方式还原三维世界，带来前所未有的可能性。</span></p>\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">应用方面，从创意设计（家具、电影、营销物料）到电商和娱乐，空间智能AI能降低创作门槛，普及技术。在教育领域，3D模型能革新教学方式，如讲解太阳系。在专业培训（体育、外科手术、烹饪）中也蕴含巨大机遇。</span></p>\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">最重要的是</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">机器人技术</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。无论是人形机器人还是自动驾驶汽车等自主行动的智能体，要在现实世界中自如行动（如换灯泡、救灾），都需要具备空间感知能力，理解周围环境。</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这已不只是语言的问题，而是需要全新的表达维度，探索空间智能和三维表达的全新可能。</span></span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">未来是否会出现集大语言模型、视觉模型、空间感知能力，甚至结合机器人技术的基础模型？</span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">绝对有可能！我们World Labs就在开发针对空间智能和3D生成的基础模型。虽然构建统一的超级大模型需要巨大资源，但在那之前，我们会看到专注不同领域、具备多模态能力的基础模型涌现。</span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">空间感知系统有哪些大家尚未充分认识到的实际应用价值？</span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">最被忽视的一点是，3D本质上就是计算机的一种编程语言。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">平面图像丢失了大量信息，难以进行精确测量、阴影添加、视角转换、遮挡处理、光线调整或物体增删等操作。掌握三维空间感知能力后，这些问题将迎刃而解。</span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">World Labs大规模世界建模的愿景是什么？</span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n           <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n            <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">应用场景极其广泛，从创意设计到机器人、教育、医疗、工业、农业等。全球市场在媒体娱乐、游戏、AR/VR等领域潜力巨大。从技术角度看，打造世界模型和3D空间智能模型是当前</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">生成式AI</span></span><span leaf=\"\">爆发中最关键的底层拼图，蕴含着改变游戏规则的巨大机遇。</span></p>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n         <section style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">\n          <h2 style=\"color:#7A9E9F;font-weight:500;margin-top:35px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.4;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5;\"><span leaf=\"\">06 AI生态洞察：开源、科研创新与信息辨识</span></h2>\n          <section style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n           <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n            <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n            <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n             <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">目前AI领域最让您眼前一亮的突破有哪些？</span></p>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n           <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n            <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n            <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n             <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">首先是</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">开源生态</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的蓬勃发展，全球参与为行业注入了新活力。其次是</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI推动科研创新</span></span><span leaf=\"\">的巨大潜力，尤其在大学等基础研究场所，AI能成为跨学科研究的得力工具，推动科学发现。</span></p>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n           <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n            <span style=\"color:#8B9BAA;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #8B9BAA;\"><span leaf=\"\">Duncan Gilchrist</span></span>\n            <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n             <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">学术界更看重长期发展，但社交媒体充斥着快节奏内容。您如何辨别真正的技术进步与炒作？</span></p>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n           <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n            <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n            <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n             <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">“北极星”的指引帮助我看穿炒作。同时，尊重专业知识和真才实学至关重要，要考量信息来源的可靠性。在信息泛滥的AI时代，</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我最担忧的是公共教育的缺失，导致大众难以辨别信息，防范虚假和误导信息。</span></span><span leaf=\"\">虽然斯坦福HAI等机构在努力，但关于AI的可靠科普仍然太少，这可能加剧信息鸿沟。</span></p>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n           <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n            <span style=\"color:#8B9BAA;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #8B9BAA;\"><span leaf=\"\">Duncan Gilchrist</span></span>\n            <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n             <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">除了教育，构建健康AI生态还需要哪些关键要素？开源和学术研究扮演什么角色？</span></p>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n           <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n            <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n            <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n             <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">一个健康的创新生态能带来多方共赢，如同美国二战后政府对公私部门的投入催生了科技繁荣。如今AI的突破也得益于数十年的基础研究积累。保持创新生态的活力至关重要，这不仅关乎资金，更关乎</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">人才培养</span></span><span leaf=\"\">和发展机会。</span></p>\n             <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我担忧的是，目前大部分AI资源集中在少数私营大公司手中，这对整个创新环境、教育体系和社会的长期发展不利。</span></span></p>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n          <section style=\"margin-bottom:30px;\">\n           <h2 style=\"color:#7A9E9F;font-weight:500;margin-top:35px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:22px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;line-height:1.4;padding-bottom:8px;border-bottom:1px solid #E5E5E5;\"><span leaf=\"\">07 AI的未来展望与发展智慧</span></h2>\n           <section style=\"margin-top:10px;margin-bottom:10px;\">\n            <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n             <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n             <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">未来回看现在，AI会被视为互联网、电脑级别的发明，还是文字、工业革命级别的突破？</span></p>\n             </section>\n            </section>\n            <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n             <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n             <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">我认为AI更像是</span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;background-color:rgba(255,193,7,0.3);padding:0 3px;border-radius:2px;\"><span leaf=\"\">电力和电脑的结合体</span></span><span leaf=\"\">。它代表了全新的计算方式，未来所有带计算功能的设备都离不开AI；同时，它具有电力的通用性，将彻底改变每个人的生活，成为社会的基础设施。我们尚处于早期阶段，但各国政府已开始大力投入，这是2022年底以来最重要的变化之一。</span></p>\n             </section>\n            </section>\n            <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n             <span style=\"color:#8B9BAA;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #8B9BAA;\"><span leaf=\"\">Duncan Gilchrist</span></span>\n             <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">在AI飞速发展的当下，对技术人员最实用的经验法则是什么？</span></p>\n             </section>\n            </section>\n            <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n             <span style=\"color:#7EB8AE;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #7EB8AE;\"><span leaf=\"\">李飞飞</span></span>\n             <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">对技术人员而言，核心价值是追求真相、尊重事实，但切忌将自己视为真理本身。</span><span style=\"background-color:rgba(108,99,255,0.12);padding:2px 8px;margin:2px 0;font-weight:500;border-radius:3px;box-shadow:0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);line-height:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们要保持谦卑，不忘初心，警惕AI过热可能带来的自我膨胀。</span></span></p>\n              <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">对政策制定者，我有几点建议：</span></p>\n              <ul style=\"padding-left:1.8em;margin:16px 0;list-style-position:outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n               <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;padding-left:0.3em;line-height:1.6;\">\n                <section>\n                 <span leaf=\"\">政策应基于科学事实，而非科幻情节或未经证实的推测。</span>\n                </section></li>\n               <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;padding-left:0.3em;line-height:1.6;\">\n                <section>\n                 <span leaf=\"\">监管应务实，重点关注实际产生影响的应用环节，而非基础研究阶段。借鉴现有行业标准（如FDA对医疗器械的管理），用AI技术优化监管，而非阻碍创新。</span>\n                </section></li>\n               <li style=\"margin-bottom:10px;padding-left:0.3em;line-height:1.6;\">\n                <section>\n                 <span leaf=\"\">确保整个行业生态获得足够的资源支持，平衡大企业发展与初创企业、公共部门研究的活力，促进社会长远发展。</span>\n                </section></li>\n              </ul>\n             </section>\n            </section>\n            <section style=\"margin: 20px 0;\">\n             <span style=\"color:#A9937B;font-weight:600;font-size:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:5px;padding-left:12px;line-height:1.4;border-left:4px solid #A9937B;\"><span leaf=\"\">Hugo Bowne-Anderson</span></span>\n             <section style=\"margin-top:5px;line-height:1.8;\">\n              <p style=\"margin:12px 0;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(51,51,51,0.9);\"><span leaf=\"\">非常感谢您为我们描绘了构建更健康人工智能生态体系的清晰蓝图。汽车安全带最初以男性为标准，后逐步完善，这个例子很好地诠释了我们需要系统化思维来解决技术发展中的普适性问题。</span></p>\n             </section>\n            </section>\n           </section>\n          </section>\n         </section>\n        </section>\n       </section>\n      </section>\n     </section>\n    </section>\n   </section>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n \n",
  "aiSummary": "李飞飞对话：AI 是文明级技术，需以人为本发展，空间智能是未来前沿。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "李飞飞对话：AI 是文明级技术，需以人为本发展，空间智能是未来前沿。",
  "summary": "本文总结了《High Signal》播客对斯坦福 HAI 联合主任李飞飞的深度访谈。李飞飞在访谈中强调，AI 是一项足以改变人类文明的技术，其发展核心必须坚守“以人为本”原则，涵盖个体尊严、社群赋能和社会公平。她分享了好奇心与科技向善如何指引其科研道路，并回顾了 ImageNet、HAI 成立等关键节点。访谈重点探讨了空间智能作为 AI 下一重要前沿的潜力，及其在机器人、教育、创意等三维世界应用中的重要性。此外，李飞飞分析了构建健康 AI 生态系统的要素，包括平衡公私部门投入、重视基础研究、人才培养和开源社区，并强调了公众 AI 教育及信息辨别能力的重要性。最后，她将 AI 类比为电力和电脑的结合体，并对技术人员和政策制定者提出了基于事实、注重实效的务实建议。",
